---
description: Testing rules
globs: packages/frontend-core/src/__tests__/integration/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

- Prefer single logical expect/assert per test
- Do not create many tests without need, prefer one complex test
- Integration test: Use the semantic API provided by `ui` for common actions instead of manual DOM queries.

## Run Integration Tests

```bash
# Run specific integration test file
cd packages/frontend-core
pnpm test src/__tests__/integration/resourceJump.integration.test.tsx

# Or from root using nx
nx run @env-hopper/frontend-core:test:unit -- src/__tests__/integration/resourceJump.integration.test.tsx
```

## Quick Commands

```bash
# All frontend-core tests (including integration)
pnpm run test:frontend-core
```
